EAST shows some extra strength plus a 5-card \C suit with his 4\C bid. 

When WEST's Blackwood discovers two Aces in EAST's hand she goes right to 7\S. 
She knows EAST has only three red cards and her \HA 
\D A K will take care of them. She figures EAST can ruff 
out any \C losers.}

